---
title: "checkUpkeep (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: load feeAggregator, allowlisted assets
    q_init --> q_loop: for each asset in allowlisted assets
    q_loop --> q_get_params: assetParams = s_assetParams[asset]
    q_get_params --> q_loop: decimals == 0 (skip unconfigured)
    q_get_params --> q_get_price: decimals > 0
    q_get_price --> q_check_assetout: (assetPrice, isPriceValid) = _getAssetPrice(asset)
    q_check_assetout --> q_set_out_valid: asset == s_assetOut
    q_set_out_valid --> q_check_live: isAssetOutPriceValid = isPriceValid
    q_check_assetout --> q_check_live: asset != s_assetOut
    q_check_live --> q_check_ended: auctionStart != 0 (live auction)
    q_check_live --> q_check_eligible: auctionStart == 0 AND isPriceValid
    q_check_live --> q_loop: auctionStart == 0 AND !isPriceValid
    q_check_ended --> q_mark_ended: duration expired OR (isPriceValid AND balance < minAuctionSize)
    q_mark_ended --> q_loop: add to endedAuctions
    q_check_ended --> q_loop: auction still live
    q_check_eligible --> q_calc_value: availableBalance = balanceOf(feeAggregator)
    q_calc_value --> q_mark_eligible: usdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_mark_eligible --> q_loop: add to eligibleAssets
    q_calc_value --> q_loop: usdValue < minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_loop --> q_filter: all assets processed
    q_filter --> q_encode: clear eligibleAssets if !isAssetOutPriceValid
    q_encode --> [*]: return (upkeepNeeded, performData)

    note right of q_check_live
        INV-001: No new auctions start when assetOut price is invalid
        INV-002: Auction ends when duration expires or balance drops below minimum
        INV-003: Only assets with valid prices and sufficient balance are eligible
    end note
